# AlexaIOT for Windows IOT

Features::

 * Voice activation - Say Hello or Alexa to activate her
 * Very basic Alexa authorization protocol (API V1) and about 15% API v20160207 (API2)
 * Basic response handling
 * Audio player / Audio recorder
 * Badly written code <- My treat!

